OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776103864
OL,3,CDeer in Oxfordshire freed after
OL,4,Cbecoming entangled in rope
OL,6,FA deer has died and another has been
OL,7,Fsuccessfully released by the RSPCA
OL,8,Fafter becoming entangled in rope in
OL,9,FSonning Common.
OL,11,FThe incident involved two bucks whose
OL,12,Fantlers had become tangled together,
OL,13,Fafter becoming caught in rope.
OL,15,FAnimal Rescue Officers Chelsea Dale,
OL,16,Fand Marie Stevens from the RSPCA's
OL,17,FCasualty Animal Specialist Team, were
OL,18,Fcalled to the scene on 21 March, by a
OL,19,Fpasser-by who spotted the animals'
OL,20,Fplight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
